<h1 class="header-project">Chef Club:<br />learn and love cooking!</h1>
<section class="google" style="padding-bottom:4em;">
  <p>For my presentation, I chose to go with option #2, to teach others about a topic I'm passionate about. I love cooking, and delicious food. I want to share that with the world. I believe that everything can be broken down into simpler steps, and by following the basic steps (like a checklist) and applying them, you can learn anything.</p>

  <p>I like to call this idea Chef Club. It's an easy, focused way to learn cooking by focusing on one meal per week. It shows you what we're cooking, the recipe, the ingredient, and the ability for community members to share their experiences. Each week a new recipe is put online. Focus is powerful, so I use that to my advantage to keep people interested by only showing 1 recipe per week.</p>

